OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the Southport
OL,7,FInquiry Figen Murrary, the mum of
OL,8,FMartyn Hett, says the Manchester Arena
OL,9,FInquiry gave her the answers she
OL,10,Fneeded, but it took an emotional and
OL,11,Fphysical toll.
OL,13,FThe government has so far announced
OL,14,Fthree new public inquiries in 2025,
OL,15,Fbringing the total of ongoing or
OL,16,Fannounced inquiries to 21. But with
OL,17,Fmore public inquiries than ever - are
OL,18,Fthey working as they should?
