OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,FFigen Murray OBE, the mother of Martyn
OL,7,FHett, one of 22 people killed in the
OL,8,FManchester Arena bombing, knows all
OL,9,Ftoo well the emotional and physical
OL,10,Ftoll public inquiries can take on
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,FThe inquiry into the Manchester Arena
OL,14,FAttack lasted more than three years.
OL,16,FShe said: "Going through an inquiry as
OL,17,Fa family member who has been directly
OL,18,Faffected either by death or injury, it
OL,19,Fis one of the most traumatic
OL,20,Fexperiences I have ever gone through.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
