OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,F"Once you see something, you can't un-
OL,7,Fsee it. And when you hear things you
OL,8,Fcan't un-hear them. So people need to
OL,9,Fappreciate that sitting through an
OL,10,Finquiry you see things, you hear
OL,11,Fthings, you go through all sorts of
OL,12,Femotions and it's brutal."
OL,14,FHowever Figen maintains the inquiry
OL,15,Fdid give her the answers she needed
OL,16,Fand helped her campaign for Martyn's
OL,17,FLaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
