OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,FWhile few will disagree with the need
OL,7,Ffor an inquiry into the Southport
OL,8,Ftragedy, some remain skeptical as to
OL,9,Fwhat it'll achieve.
OL,11,F"It had been hoped Southport would be
OL,12,Fthe first to adhere to the
OL,13,FHillsborough Law which would force
OL,14,Fpublic officials to tell the truth at
OL,15,Finquiries from the outset or face
OL,16,Fcriminal sanctions but the bill's yet
OL,17,Fto be passed."
OL,19,FElkan Abrahamson, Director of
OL,20,FHillsborough Law Now believes the
OL,21,Fcurrent inquiry process is ineffective.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
