OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,F"Time and again we have a public
OL,7,Finquiry where recommendations are made
OL,8,Fand just ignored and we have to do
OL,9,Fsomething about that."
OL,11,FBut Professor Lucy Easthope, one of
OL,12,Fthe country's leading emergency
OL,13,Fplanners, believes if done well the
OL,14,FSouthport Inquiry could bring positive
OL,15,Fchange.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
