OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,F"One of the things about the inquiry
OL,7,Fis there wasn't a trial which many
OL,8,Fpeople were relieved about in some
OL,9,Fways but it did mean there were a lot
OL,10,Fof questions unanswered and the
OL,11,Finquiry can go much more broadly into
OL,12,Fother questions as well," she said.
OL,14,F"There is no doubt that inquiries done
OL,15,Fwell with the right disclosure and
OL,16,Fwith a very focused chair that demands
OL,17,Fthings of the people giving evidence
OL,18,Fdoes inevitably and necessarily change
OL,19,Fpractise.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
