OL,3,CCan public inquiries lead to real
OL,4,Cchange?
OL,6,F"The sad thing for us is to have to
OL,7,Fsee it being in an inquiry. "
OL,9,FSo it seems this public inquiry will
OL,10,Fitself come in for intense scrutiny.
OL,11,FThe big question, will be whether
OL,12,Fit'll be able to provide clarity and a
OL,13,Fdegree of closure to the families of
OL,14,FAlice, Bebe and Elsie and all the
OL,15,Fothers affected by the terrible events
OL,16,Fof last summer.
